 .NET Passport at a participating Web site. 

Use the e-mail address (craig.dean@enron.com) and password you provided during registration to sign in instantly at any .NET Passport-enabled Web site that displays the .NET Passport sign-in button. 

If you also created a Passport wallet, you can use it to make faster, easier purchases at sites that offer the Passport express purchase service. (If you didn't create a Passport wallet and you would like to, we'll tell you how below.) 

